Look, it's me, I'm here. Deal with it. Let's move on.

167
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:54,580
我只是…
I just...

168
00:13:54,710 --> 00:13:56,080
-别说了 -好吧 我不说了
-Drop it. -All right, I'll drop it.

169
00:13:56,210 --> 00:13:59,670
这是罗德中校收集到…
I have before me a complete report on the Iron Man weapon,

170
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:02,420
有关钢铁侠武器的完整报告
compiled by Colonel Rhodes. And, Colonel, for the record,

171
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:05,630
中校 请你念57页第4段
can you please read page 57, paragraph four?

172
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:08,010
你要我念特定的段落
You're requesting that I read specific selections

173
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,390
-是报告中的 议员？ -是的
-from my report, Senator? -Yes, sir.

174
00:14:09,470 --> 00:14:11,390
我以为我是来做…
It was my understanding that I was going to be testifying

175
00:14:11,470 --> 00:14:13,640
完整及详细的报告
in a much more comprehensive and detailed manner.

176
00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:15,350
我了解 但是今天有很多变数
l understand. A lot of things have changed today.

177
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,730
-假如你能读一下… -你懂的
-So if you could just read... -You do understand

178
00:14:16,810 --> 00:14:19,230
光是念出那一个段落不能代表…
that reading a single paragraph out of context does not reflect

179
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:22,610
-我的完整报告…  -请你念出来 中校 我懂 谢谢
-the summary of my final... -Just read it, Colonel. I do. Thank you.

180
00:14:23,650 --> 00:14:25,070
好吧
Very well.

181
00:14:26,990 --> 00:14:30,280
“由于钢铁侠并不隶属政府任何单位
"As he does not operate within any definable branch of government,

182
00:14:32,290 --> 00:14:36,370
钢铁侠具有潜在的安全隐患 对于国家
"Iron Man presents a potential threat to the security of both the nation

183
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:37,870
以及国家的利益来说”
"and to her interests."

184
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,830
但是我的结论是…
I did, however, go on to summarise

185
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:42,630
钢铁侠的好处远比坏处更多
that the benefits of Iron Man far outweigh the liabilities.

186
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:44,880
-并且符合我们利益的是…  -够了 中校
-And that it would be in our interest... -That's enough, Colonel.

187
00:14:44,970 --> 00:14:46,130
-让斯塔克先生… -我说够了
-...to fold Mr Stark... -That's enough.

188
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,760
…加入军事指挥体系 议员
...into the existing chain of command, Senator.

189
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:51,220
我不喜欢加入任何体系 但我倒是可以考虑当国防部长
I'm not a joiner, but I'll consider Secretary of Defense, if you ask nice.

190
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:53,970
我可以减少工作时数
We can amend the hours a little bit.

191
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,390
如果可能 我还想继续播放
I'd like to go on and show, if I may,

192
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,650
你报告中的影像
the imagery that's connected to your report.

193
00:14:58,770 --> 00:15:01,610
我认为目前还不是…
I believe it is somewhat premature to reveal these images

194
00:15:01,690 --> 00:15:03,480
-向大众公开这些影像的时候 -恕我直言
-to the general public at this time. -With all due respect,

195
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:04,780
我能理解 中校
Colonel, I understand.

196
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:08,950
但如果你能描述这些影像 我们会非常感激
And if you could just narrate those for us, we'd be very grateful.

197
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:10,990
把影像调出来
Let's have the images.

198
00:15:12,450 --> 00:15:15,660
情报显示这些影像中的装置
Intelligence suggests that the devices seen in these photos

199
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:20,170
其实是斯塔克先生钢铁盔甲的仿冒品
are, in fact, attempts at making manned copies of Mr Stark's suit.

200
00:15:20,290 --> 00:15:25,300
这一点经过我们的盟国以及地面情报单位的证实
This has been corroborated by our allies and local intelligence on the ground,

201
00:15:25,380 --> 00:15:30,510
这些钢铁盔甲目前很可能可以使用
indicating that these suits are quite possibly, at this moment, operational.

202
00:15:30,930 --> 00:15:34,600
等一下 给我看看 有东西了
Hold on one second, buddy. Let me see something here.

203
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:38,180
我真厉害 我控制了你的屏幕
Boy, I'm good. I commandeered your screens.

204
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,690
我需要它们 该让这一切透明化了
I need them. Time for a little transparency.

205
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:43,690
-我们看看这到底是怎么回事 -他在做什么？
-Now, let's see what's really going on. -What is he doing?

206
00:15:43,770 --> 00:15:47,030
请你们看电脑屏幕
If you will direct your attention to said screens...

207
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:48,700
我相信那是北韩
l believe that's North Korea.

208
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:59,790
能不能关掉？快关掉
Can you turn that off? Take it off.

209
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,040
伊朗
Iran.

210
00:16:04,550 --> 00:16:08,550
没有紧急严重的威胁 那是贾斯汀・汉默吗？
No grave immediate threat here. Is that Justin Hammer?

211
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:11,090
他怎么也在搞仿冒品？
How did Hammer get in the game?

212
00:16:11,890 --> 00:16:13,800
贾斯汀 你上电视了 焦点人物
Justin, you're on TV. Focus up.

213
00:16:15,970 --> 00:16:18,390
很好 向左转 很好 向右转
Okay, give me a left twist. Left's good. Turn to the right.

214
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:23,520
糟了 糟了！
Oh, shit. Oh, shit!

215
00:16:25,730 --> 00:16:29,530
大部份的国家得花5到10年
Yeah, I'd say most countries, five, 10 years away.

216
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:30,900
汉默工业至少要花20年
Hammer Industries, 20.

217
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:33,620
容我指出那位驾驶员没有死
I'd like to point out that that test pilot survived.

218
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,240
我想我们看够了 他证明了他的看法
I think we're done, is the point that he's making.

219
00:16:35,330 --> 00:16:38,540
-我觉得没有任何理由… -我猜我只能说：不客气
-I don't think there's any reason... -The point is, you're welcome, I guess.

220
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:41,460
-什么意思？ -我能防止核战的恫吓
-For what? -Because I'm your nuclear deterrent.

221
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:44,080
钢铁侠很有用 我们很安全 美国很安全
It's working. We're safe. America is secure.

222
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:46,090
你要我的产品？想都别想！
You want my property? You can't have it.

223
00:16:46,170 --> 00:16:47,590
不过我帮了你们个大忙
But I did you a big favour.

224
00:16:48,340 --> 00:16:51,260
我一个人就能维持世界和平
I've successfully privatized world peace.

225
00:16:54,090 --> 00:16:56,640
你还想要我怎样？现在就是这样！
What more do you want? For now!

226
00:16:57,680 --> 00:17:00,310
我试着和那些跳梁小丑合作
I tried to play ball with these ass-clowns.

227
00:17:00,430 --> 00:17:03,770
…去你的 斯塔克先生
...you, Mr Stark. ...you, buddy.

228
00:17:04,020 --> 00:17:05,980
散会 今天散会
We're adjourned. We're adjourned for today.

229
00:17:06,110 --> 00:17:08,360
-好吧 -你真是个开心果
-Okay. -You've been a delight.

230
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,450
听好 我全是为了人民
My bond is with the people.

231
00:17:16,530 --> 00:17:21,790
我以自己的乐趣为国家服务
And I will serve this great nation at the pleasure of myself.

232
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:23,460
如果我向全世界证明了什么
If there's one thing I've proven

233
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:26,880
那就是你们绝对能信赖我…能让自己很高兴
it's that you can count on me to pleasure myself.

234
00:17:57,490 --> 00:17:59,610
（加州马里布）

235
00:18:02,580 --> 00:18:04,080
醒醒吧 老爹回来了
Wake up. Daddy's home.

236
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,750
欢迎回家
Welcome home, sir.

237
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:07,710
恭喜博览会开幕仪式
Congratulations on the opening ceremonies.

238
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:10,840
以及参议院听证会大大地成功
They were such a success, as was your Senate hearing.

239
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,670
容我说一句
And may I say how refreshing it is

240
00:18:12,760 --> 00:18:16,510
你穿着衣服上电视令人耳目一新
to finally see you in a video with your clothing on, sir.

241
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:19,550
你！
You!

242
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:22,350
我发誓我会把你拆掉 我会泡烂你的主板
I swear to God I'll dismantle you. I'll soak your motherboard.

243
00:18:22,430 --> 00:18:25,020
我会把你做成书架
I'll turn you into a wine rack.

244
00:18:25,560 --> 00:18:28,940
这种臭东西我还要喝多少？
How many ounces a day of this gobbledegook am I supposed to drink?

245
00:18:29,020 --> 00:18:33,030
80盎斯才能消除钯中毒的征状
We are up to 80 ounces a day to counteract the symptoms, sir.

246
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:35,950
检查钯元素含量
Check palladium levels.

247
00:18:37,870 --> 00:18:40,200
血液毒性：24%
Blood toxicity, 24%.

248
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:44,040
看来只要你继续使用钢铁盔甲
It appears that the continued use of the Iron Man suit

249
00:18:44,120 --> 00:18:46,540
中毒的速度会愈快
is accelerating your condition.

250
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:50,420
另一块钯能量板又耗损光了
Another core has been depleted.

251
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,470
它们耗损得很快
God, they're running out quick.

252
00:18:55,550 --> 00:18:58,220
我模拟过每一种已知的元素
I have run simulations on every known element,

253
00:18:58,300 --> 00:19:02,430
没有一种能替代钯元素
and none can serve as a viable replacement for the palladium core.

254
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:07,730
你的时闲和选择已经不多了
You are running out of both time and options.

255
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:14,150
很不幸 让你活命的装置
Unfortunately, the device that's keeping you alive

256
00:19:14,230 --> 00:19:16,070
也会害死你
is also killing you.

257
00:19:17,570 --> 00:19:18,990
波兹小姐来了
Miss Potts is approaching.

258
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:21,990
-我建议你立刻告诉… -静音
-I recommend that you inform her... -Mute.

259
00:19:25,080 --> 00:19:26,660
你在开玩笑吗？
Is this a joke?

260
00:19:28,080 --> 00:19:29,750
-你在想什么？ -什么？
-What are you thinking? -What?

261
00:19:29,830 --> 00:19:32,130
-你在想什么？ -我在想我很忙
-What are you thinking? -Hey, I'm thinking I'm busy.

262
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:34,550
你又在生气
And you're angry about something.

263
00:19:34,630 --> 00:19:36,010
你感冒了吗？我不想被传染
Do you have the sniffles? I don't wanna get sick.

264
00:19:36,090 --> 00:19:37,510
-你是不是把… -继续做你的事
-Did you just donate... -Keep your business.

265
00:19:37,590 --> 00:19:41,140
我们所有的现代艺术收藏捐给…
...our entire modern art collection to the...

266
00:19:41,260 --> 00:19:42,850
-美国童子军协会 -美国童子军协会？
-Boy Scouts ofAmerica. -...Boy Scouts ofAmerica?

267
00:19:42,930 --> 00:19:44,720
那是很有意义的组织
Yes. It is a worthwhile organisation.

268
00:19:44,810 --> 00:19:48,180
我没有亲自检查过木箱 不过基本上没错
I didn't physically check the crates but, basically, yes.

269
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:50,440
而且不是我们的收藏 是我的收藏 不要介意
And it's not "our" collection, it's my collection. No offence.

270
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:54,230
不会 你知道吗？我有权讨论“我们”的收藏
No, you know what? I think I'm actually entitled to say "our" collection

271
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:57,530
因为我花了十年整理
considering the time that I put in, over 10 years, curating that.

272
00:19:57,610 --> 00:19:59,450
都是为了减税 我需要那个
It was a tax write-off. I needed that.

273
00:19:59,530 --> 00:20:02,620
我只有8千零11件事…
You know, there's only about 8,011 things

274
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:04,660
必须跟你讨论
that I really need to talk to you about.

275
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:06,200
机械手 别恍神 专心点
Dummy. Hey, stop spacing out.

276
00:20:06,290 --> 00:20:07,750
布里奇伯特已经加工了部分
The Bridgeport's already machining that part.

277
00:20:07,830 --> 00:20:10,210
博览会完全是浪费时闲
The Expo is a gigantic waste of time.

278
00:20:10,290 --> 00:20:12,540
你感冒没好之前得戴口罩
I need you to wear a surgical mask until you're feeling better.

279
00:20:12,630 --> 00:20:13,670
-好不好？ -你很没礼貌
-Is that okay? -That's rude.

280
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:15,250
没有什么比博览会对我更重要
There's nothing more important to me than the Expo.

281
00:20:15,340 --> 00:20:16,670
那是我最关心的事情
It's my primary point of concern.

282
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:19,920
-不知你为何… -博览会只是你的虚荣心作祟
-I don't know why you're... -The Expo is your ego gone crazy.

283
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:21,800
哇 你看看
Wow. Look at that.

284
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:25,390
这是现代艺术 我要挂起来
That's modern art. That's going up.

285
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:28,220
-你一定是在开玩笑 -我要马上把它挂起来
-You've got to be kidding. -I'm gonna put this up right now.

286
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:30,520
-这很重要 -斯塔克工业乱成一团
-This is vital. -Stark is in complete disarray.

287
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:32,940
-你明白吗？ -不对 我们的股价涨停板
-You understand that? -No. Our stocks have never been higher.

288
00:20:33,020 --> 00:20:35,360
-那是从经营者的角度来看 -你…如果很乱
-Yes, from a managerial standpoint. -You are... Well, if it's messy,

289
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,940
-那就绕回去 -让我举例说明
-then let's double back. -Let me give you an example.

290
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:38,610
-再谈刚才那件事 -不 不
-Let's move on to another subject. -No, no, no, no.

291
00:20:38,690 --> 00:20:40,400
你不准把巴奈特・纽曼的画拿下来
You are not taking down the Barnett Newman

292
00:20:40,490 --> 00:20:41,990
-继续挂着！ -我不是拿下来
-and hanging that up! -I'm not taking it down.

293
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:43,320
只是取代它
I'm just replacing it with this.

294
00:20:43,410 --> 00:20:44,780
-看看我得到了什么 -好吧 随你便
-Let's see what I can get going here. -Okay, fine.

295
00:20:44,870 --> 00:20:47,990
我想说的是…我们拿到合约
My point is, we have already awarded contracts

296
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,750
-风力发电场的合约 -别提到风
-to the wind farm people. -Yeah. Don't say "wind farm."

297
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:51,910
-你会害我撇风 -还有废气处理厂的合约
-I'm already feeling gassy. -And to the plastic plantation tree,

298
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,130
那是你的点子 这些人都领我们的薪水
which was your idea, by the way. Those people are on payroll...

299
00:20:54,210 --> 00:20:56,000
-一切都是我的点子 -…你不会再做决定
-Everything was my idea. -...and you won't make a decision.

300
00:20:56,090 --> 00:20:57,800
我不再关心自由派议题了
I don't care about the liberal agenda any more.

301
00:20:57,880 --> 00:21:00,260
超无聊的！我要给你一个无聊警告
It's boring. Boring. I'm giving you a boring alert.

302
00:21:00,340 --> 00:21:02,630
-你去做  -做什么？
-You do it. -I do what?

303
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:04,680
这点子太赞了 我刚想出来的 你来管理公司
Excellent idea. I just figured this out. You run the company.

304
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:06,160
是啊 我一直在试着管理公司
Yeah, I'm trying to run the company.

305
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,560
小辣椒 我需要你管理公司
Pepper, I need you to run the company.

306
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:09,060
