311
00:21:15,230 --> 00:21:17,150
-不 你都没在听 -我要你当首席执行官
-No, you are not listening to me. -I'm trying to make you CEO.

312
00:21:17,230 --> 00:21:19,110
你为什么不肯？
Why won't you let me?

313
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:22,650
-你喝了不少吧？ -叶绿素汁
-Have you been drinking? -Chlorophyll.

314
00:21:24,570 --> 00:21:28,830
我正式任命你为斯塔克工业首席执行官
I hereby irrevocably appoint you chairman and CEO of Stark Industries,

315
00:21:28,910 --> 00:21:30,830
马上生效
effective immediately.

316
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,920
就这样
Yeah, done deal. Okay?

317
00:21:36,380 --> 00:21:38,960
信不信由你 我想了很久
I've actually given this a fair amount of thought,

318
00:21:39,050 --> 00:21:42,970
我甚至找了一些人选
believe it or not. Doing a bit of headhunting, so to speak,

319
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:46,930
认真思考谁是最适合的人选
trying to figure out who a worthy successor would be.

320
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:48,810
后来才发现…
And then I realised

321
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:53,890
就是你 一直都是你
it's you. It's always been you.

322
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:57,020
我还以为会有法律问题
I thought there'd be a legal issue,

323
00:21:57,110 --> 00:22:00,570
不过我是可以指定我的接班人
but actually I'm capable of appointing my successor.

324
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:03,280
也就是你
My successor being you.

325
00:22:05,450 --> 00:22:07,120
恭喜了
