西南区有比你更大的问题
I have bigger problems than you in the southwest region to deal with.

827
01:03:19,670 --> 01:03:20,710
打针吧
Hit him.

828
01:03:21,920 --> 01:03:25,260
你们是要拿走我的肾脏去卖吗？
Oh, God, are you gonna steal my kidney and sell it?

829
01:03:25,720 --> 01:03:28,640
可不可以别再做这些怪事
Could you please not do anything awful for five seconds?

830
01:03:29,220 --> 01:03:32,850
-她刚才对我做了什么？ -我们是为了你好
-What did she just do to me? -What did we just do for you?

831
01:03:32,930 --> 01:03:35,350
那是二氧化锂 能减缓你的病征
That's lithium dioxide. It's gonna take the edge off.

832
01:03:35,440 --> 01:03:37,310
我们想让你回去工作
We're trying to get you back to work.

833
01:03:37,400 --> 01:03:39,480
再给我两盒我就会好起来
Give me a couple of boxes of that. I'll be right as rain.

834
01:03:39,560 --> 01:03:41,480
那不是解药 只能减缓病征
It's not a cure, it just abates the symptoms.

835
01:03:41,570 --> 01:03:44,070
看来要治好你并不容易
Doesn't look like it's gonna be an easy fix.

836
01:03:44,150 --> 01:03:46,360
相信我 我知道 我了解状况
Trust me, I know. I'm good at this stuff.

837
01:03:46,450 --> 01:03:48,820
我一直在找钯元素的替代品
I've been looking for a suitable replacement for palladium.

838
01:03:48,910 --> 01:03:53,330
我试过每种元素的每种组合
I've tried every combination, every permutation of every known element.

839
01:03:53,410 --> 01:03:56,500
我是来告诉你 你还没全部试过
Well, I'm here to tell you, you haven't tried them all.

840
01:03:57,960 --> 01:04:01,080
你有快递！
Hey, hey, hey. Special delivery.

841
01:04:01,170 --> 01:04:02,710
使命必达！
Candygram.

842
01:04:06,920 --> 01:04:08,380
我带了东西给你
I brought you something.

843
01:04:08,970 --> 01:04:10,720
没错
Oh, yeah.

844
01:04:13,260 --> 01:04:15,100
我们找到你的小鸟 兄弟！
We got you the bird, pal.

845
01:04:15,180 --> 01:04:16,520
这不是我的小鸟
This is not my bird.

846
01:04:16,930 --> 01:04:19,020
什么意思？这就是那只小鸟
What do you mean? That's the bird. This is the bird.

847
01:04:19,100 --> 01:04:21,900
我靠很多关系才找到的
Yeah. Pulled a lot of strings to get this bird.

848
01:04:21,980 --> 01:04:23,270
这是只很棒的小鸟
This is a great bird.

849
01:04:23,360 --> 01:04:25,980
-而且很漂亮 -大老远从俄罗斯找来的
-It's a beautiful bird. -We got this all the way from Russia.

850
01:04:26,070 --> 01:04:28,530
老兄 这不是我的小鸟
Hey, man, this not my bird.

851
01:04:30,870 --> 01:04:34,790
嗯听着 就算不是你那只小鸟 这只小鸟也很漂亮
Well, listen, even if it's not the bird, I mean, this is a gorgeous bird.

852
01:04:34,870 --> 01:04:37,660
别这么固执
I mean, you know, look, don't get so attached to things.

853
01:04:37,750 --> 01:04:39,460
你得学会放手
Learn to let go.

854
01:04:42,210 --> 01:04:44,710
等一下 杰克 那是什么？
Wait a minute. Jack, what is that?

855
01:04:45,250 --> 01:04:48,380
那…那不是头盔 那是什么？
Is that... That's not a helmet. What is that?

856
01:04:56,890 --> 01:05:00,440
伊万？那是什么？杰克
Ivan... What's this? Jack.

857
01:05:01,400 --> 01:05:03,440
那是头盔吗？看起来不像
Is that a helmet? It doesn't look like a helmet to me.

858
01:05:03,520 --> 01:05:06,110
你要怎么把头塞进去？
How... How are you supposed to get a head in there?

859
01:05:06,190 --> 01:05:08,030
-杰克 你的头塞得进去吗？ -不
-Jack, could you put your head in there? -No.

860
01:05:08,110 --> 01:05:11,320
试着把头塞进去 试试看 试着塞进去
Try to put your head in there. Go ahead. Try to put your head in there.

861
01:05:11,410 --> 01:05:14,070
伊万 他的头塞不进去
See, Ivan? He can't put his head in there.

862
01:05:14,160 --> 01:05:18,540
那不是头盔 那是一颗头 我得把一个人装进去
That's... That's not a helmet. It's a head. I need to put a guy in there.

863
01:05:18,620 --> 01:05:22,000
这套钢铁盔甲要能穿 你了吗？
I need to fit a person in that suit. You understand?

864
01:05:22,330 --> 01:05:24,460
-摇控钢铁士兵比较好 -摇控钢铁士兵比较好？
-Drone better. -What? Drone better?

865
01:05:24,540 --> 01:05:27,130
为什么比较好？
Why is drone better? Why is drone better?

866
01:05:27,210 --> 01:05:29,010
人会出错
People make problem.

867
01:05:29,090 --> 01:05:30,970
相信我 摇控比较好
Trust me. Drone better.

868
01:05:31,430 --> 01:05:35,600
伊万 你知道我喜欢你 我还替你弄到小鸟
Ivan, you know, I like you. I got you the bird.

869
01:05:36,470 --> 01:05:38,310
你说没问题
You said, "No problem."

870
01:05:38,390 --> 01:05:41,310
是你说的 你说没问题
That's what you said to me. You said, "No problem."

871
01:05:41,390 --> 01:05:44,190
现在我要钢铁盔甲 政府要的是钢铁盔甲
Now I need suits. The government wants suits.

872
01:05:44,270 --> 01:05:46,270
像钢铁侠一样！你了吗？
Like Iron Man. You understand?

873
01:05:46,360 --> 01:05:49,480
那是大家要的！这样他们才高兴
That's what the people want. That's what's gonna make them happy.

874
01:05:50,320 --> 01:05:51,650
老兄
Hey, man.

875
01:05:53,200 --> 01:05:55,780
别这么固执
Don't get too attached to things.

876
01:05:56,490 --> 01:05:58,200
你得学会放手
Learn to let go.

877
01:06:01,290 --> 01:06:04,290
这些钢铁士兵最好能一炮而红
These drones better steal the show, Ivan.

878
01:06:04,920 --> 01:06:08,340
了吗？它们最好能让我出名！
You understand? Better rock my world, Ivan.

879
01:06:17,930 --> 01:06:19,600
不可思议
Unbelievable.

880
01:06:20,060 --> 01:06:22,730
这样一来参议院就不会再烦我
This ought to get the Senate off my ass.

881
01:06:22,810 --> 01:06:26,190
-它能用吗？ -完全能够执行任务
-It's functional? -Fully mission-capable.

882
01:06:26,560 --> 01:06:29,940
很好 请汉默替它装上武器
Good. Get Hammer down here to weaponize it.

883
01:06:30,940 --> 01:06:31,990
长官？
Sir?

884
01:06:32,070 --> 01:06:34,700
汉默要在博览会上展示新武器
Justin Hammer's making a weapons presentation at the Expo.

885
01:06:34,780 --> 01:06:36,410
我们要用这个来做开场
We'd like this to introduce it.

886
01:06:36,490 --> 01:06:38,070
我不认为博览会适合…
Sir, I don't believe that the Expo...

887
01:06:38,160 --> 01:06:40,950
中校 世人需要看到这玩意
Colonel, the world needs to see this fast.

888
01:06:41,040 --> 01:06:44,080
-我们必须满足他们 -是的 将军 但是…
-We've got to make this happen. -Yes, General, but...

889
01:06:44,170 --> 01:06:46,170
这也是个命令
It's also an order.

890
01:06:46,540 --> 01:06:47,880
遵命 长官
Yes, sir.

891
01:06:48,250 --> 01:06:51,710
干得好 中校 国家以你为荣
Good work, Colonel. You've made your country proud.

892
01:06:51,800 --> 01:06:53,420
谢谢你 长官
Thank you, sir.

893
01:06:59,600 --> 01:07:03,310
你胸口的那玩意是根据未完成的科技做的
That thing in your chest is based on unfinished technology.

894
01:07:03,390 --> 01:07:04,430
不 它是完成品
No, it was finished.

895
01:07:04,520 --> 01:07:08,650
我把它缩小后才起了功效
It has never been particularly effective until I miniaturised it and put it in my...

896
01:07:08,730 --> 01:07:10,860
不 你爸说方舟反应炉…
No. Howard said the arc reactor

897
01:07:10,940 --> 01:07:12,690
只是更伟大的科技的跳板
was the stepping stone to something greater.

898
01:07:12,780 --> 01:07:17,280
他当年准备展开一场能量竞争 会让所有对手望尘莫及
He was about to kick off an energy race that was gonna dwarf the arms race.

899
01:07:17,780 --> 01:07:18,910
他摸索到了一种超能量的头绪
He was on to something big,

900
01:07:18,990 --> 01:07:22,450
核子反应炉在相较之下…
something so big that it was gonna make the nuclear reactor

901
01:07:22,540 --> 01:07:24,540
会像是一枚3A电池
look like a triple-A battery.

902
01:07:24,620 --> 01:07:27,120
只有他吗？安东・万科也有参与吧？
Just him, or was Anton Vanko in on this, too?

903
01:07:27,210 --> 01:07:30,290
安东・万科就像铜板的另一面
Anton Vanko is the other side of that coin.

904
01:07:30,380 --> 01:07:32,420
他认为那是发大财的方法
Anton saw it as a way to get rich.

905
01:07:32,510 --> 01:07:34,880
你父亲发现后就把他驱逐出境
When your father found out, he had him deported.

906
01:07:34,970 --> 01:07:36,880
当老俄发现他没有用处
When the Russians found out he couldn't deliver,

907
01:07:36,970 --> 01:07:38,510
就把他下放到西伯利亚
they shipped his ass off to Siberia

908
01:07:38,590 --> 01:07:41,350
20年来过着酗酒愤世的生活
and he spent the next 20 years in a vodka-fuelled rage.

909
01:07:41,430 --> 01:07:43,970
对小孩成长不是很好
Not quite the environment you want to raise a kid in,

910
01:07:44,060 --> 01:07:48,190
你在摩纳哥遇到就是他儿子
the son you had the misfortune of crossing paths with in Monaco.

911
01:07:48,560 --> 01:07:49,900
你说我没全部试过
You told me I hadn't tried everything.

912
01:07:49,980 --> 01:07:52,190
什么意思？我没试过什么？
What do you mean I haven't tried everything? What haven't I tried?

913
01:07:52,280 --> 01:07:56,530
他说只有你有资源和智慧…
He said that you were the only person with the means and knowledge

914
01:07:56,650 --> 01:07:58,660
去完成他开始的计划
to finish what he started.

915
01:07:58,740 --> 01:08:00,240
他这么说？
He said that?

916
01:08:00,410 --> 01:08:03,030
他说的是你吗？
Are you that guy? Are you?

917
01:08:03,120 --> 01:08:08,420
如果是你…你就能解开你的心头之谜
'Cause if you are, then you can solve the riddle of your heart.

918
01:08:12,710 --> 01:08:14,170
我不知道你是怎么知道这些事
I don't know where you get your information,

919
01:08:14,260 --> 01:08:16,510
但他并不是很肯定我
but he wasn't my biggest fan.

920
01:08:16,590 --> 01:08:17,970
你记得你爸什么？
What do you remember about your dad?

921
01:08:18,050 --> 01:08:19,760
他很冷漠 重心计
He was cold, he was calculating.

922
01:08:19,840 --> 01:08:22,600
从来没说过他爱我 也从来没说过他喜欢我
He never told me he loved me. He never even told me he liked me,

923
01:08:22,680 --> 01:08:24,260
对我来说很难理解的是
so it's a little tough for me to digest

924
01:08:24,350 --> 01:08:26,810
你来告诉我说所有的未来都取决于我自己
when you're telling me he said the whole future was riding on me

925
01:08:26,890 --> 01:08:29,850
而且他把这个责任传承给我 我不明白
and he's passing it down. I don't get that.

926
01:08:29,940 --> 01:08:31,190
他最高兴的一天
You're talking about a guy whose happiest day

927
01:08:31,270 --> 01:08:32,770
是把我送到寄宿学校
was when he shipped me off to boarding school.

928
01:08:32,860 --> 01:08:33,940
并不是这样
That's not true.

929
01:08:34,030 --> 01:08:36,690
那么很显然你比我更了解我爸
Well, then, clearly you knew my dad better than I did.

930
01:08:37,110 --> 01:08:40,780
事实上没错 他是成立神盾局的成员之一
As a matter of fact, I did. He was one of the founding members of S.H.I.E.L.D.

931
01:08:40,870 --> 01:08:42,030
什么？
What?

932
01:08:42,580 --> 01:08:44,660
-我2点钟有约  -等等…
-I got a 2:00. -Wait, wait, wait, wait.

933
01:08:44,740 --> 01:08:46,290
-这是什么？  -你可以 对吧？
-What's this? -Okay, you're good, right?

934
01:08:46,370 --> 01:08:48,120
-不 我不可以 -你能解开 对吧？
-No, I'm not good. -You got this? Right? Right?

935
01:08:48,210 --> 01:08:50,080
我连要解开什么都不知道
Got what? I don't even know what I'm supposed to get.

936
01:08:50,170 --> 01:08:53,420
娜塔莎会继续在斯塔克工业卧底
Natasha will remain a floater at Stark with her cover intact.

937
01:08:53,500 --> 01:08:56,420
-你记得考森特工吧？ -记得
-You remember Agent Coulson, right? -Yeah.

938
01:08:56,840 --> 01:08:58,340
噢 托尼
And Tony,

939
01:08:59,550 --> 01:09:02,590
记住 我会盯着你
remember, I got my eye on you.

940
01:09:08,640 --> 01:09:11,900
我们已切断所有的通讯 不能对外联系
We've disabled all communications. No contact with the outside world.

941
01:09:11,980 --> 01:09:13,360
祝好运
Good luck.

942
01:09:17,440 --> 01:09:18,690
拜托
Please.

943
01:09:19,280 --> 01:09:22,490
首先 我需要做体能训练 我会在实验室工作一下
First thing, I need a little bodywork. I'll put in a little time at the lab.

944
01:09:22,570 --> 01:09:24,740
如果你能派手下到星巴克
If we could send one of your goon squad down to The Coffee Bean,

945
01:09:24,830 --> 01:09:27,410
替我买些食物和饮料就更好
Cross Creek, for a Starbucks run, or something like that, that'd be nice.

946
01:09:27,500 --> 01:09:28,620
这不是我的职责
I'm not here for that.

947
01:09:28,700 --> 01:09:30,160
福瑞局长命令我…
I've been authorised by Director Fury

948
01:09:30,250 --> 01:09:32,710
用任何手段让你留在这里
to use any means necessary to keep you on premises.

949
01:09:32,790 --> 01:09:35,420
如果你想离开或是耍什么花招
If you attempt to leave or play any games,

950
01:09:35,500 --> 01:09:38,710
我会用电晕你 然后边看《超级保姆》边看你在地上流口水
I will tase you and watch Supernanny while you drool into the carpet.

951
01:09:38,800 --> 01:09:41,050
-好吗？ -我想我明白了
-Okay? -I think I got it, yeah.

952
01:09:41,130 --> 01:09:43,010
享受你今晚的娱乐吧
Enjoy your evening's entertainment.

953
01:09:47,260 --> 01:09:49,760
“霍华德・斯塔克所有物”

954
01:10:09,370 --> 01:10:11,000
这就是它们的能量来源吗？
Think this is the power source?

955
01:10:11,080 --> 01:10:15,880
少校 这不是科学实验 专心把武器装上去 好吗？
Major, this is not a scientific exercise. Let's just focus on arming it, all right?

956
01:10:17,000 --> 01:10:18,340
是的 长官
Yes, sir.

957
01:10:18,750 --> 01:10:20,050
好！
Oh, yes!

958
01:10:20,460 --> 01:10:22,380
好！好！
Oh, yes, yes, yes.

959
01:10:22,470 --> 01:10:24,220
今天是我生日吗？
Is it my birthday?

960
01:10:24,510 --> 01:10:27,930
不是吧？你做了什么？
You got it. What did you do? What did you do?

961
01:10:31,060 --> 01:10:33,890
-这是我想的那玩意吗？ -是的
-Is this what I think it is? -Yes, it is.

962
01:10:33,980 --> 01:10:37,060
我要知道你能替我们做什么
Hammer, I want to know what you're gonna do for us.

963
01:10:37,230 --> 01:10:38,730
我要替你们做什么？
What am I going to do for you?

964
01:10:38,820 --> 01:10:41,570
我要先替你们的软件升级
Well, the first thing I'm gonna do for you is I'm gonna upgrade your software.

965
01:10:41,940 --> 01:10:44,950
-于是 其次呢 我觉得应该…  -我说的不是这个
-And then, second, I think I should... -That's not what I'm talking about.

966
01:10:45,030 --> 01:10:47,370
我说的是火力
I'm talking about firepower.

967
01:10:48,870 --> 01:10:50,950
那你就找对人了
Well, you're talking to the right guy.

968
01:10:52,250 --> 01:10:55,540
克拉里奇高科技半自动手枪 九毫米子弹
Claridge Hi-Tec, semi-automatic, 9mm pistol.

969
01:10:56,830 --> 01:10:59,170
太差了吗？我同意
Too downtown? I agree.

970
01:10:59,710 --> 01:11:01,960
M24霰弹枪 手动上膛
M24 shotgun, pump action.

971
01:11:02,590 --> 01:11:03,880
每个弹匣五发子弹
Five-round magazine.

972
01:11:03,970 --> 01:11:05,300
你知道什么？你又不是猎人
You know what? You're not a hunter.

973
01:11:05,380 --> 01:11:07,470
我在说什么？我会把它丢掉
What am I talking about? I'm getting rid of it.

974
01:11:07,550 --> 01:11:10,010
这是比利时制FN2000冲锋枪
This is the FN-2000 from Belgium.

975
01:11:10,100 --> 01:11:12,390
比利时人不是只会做松饼
They do make something better than waffles.

976
01:11:13,230 --> 01:11:15,350
太赞了 不过你好像不满意
It's beautiful, but I can tell this isn't disco enough for you,

977
01:11:15,440 --> 01:11:16,730
所以我把它放在旁边
so I'm gonna put it right here.

978
01:11:16,810 --> 01:11:19,860
这是40厘米口径榴弹枪
You're looking at a Milkor 40mm grenade launcher.

979
01:11:19,940 --> 01:11:22,980
能发射催泪弹、烟雾弹 对付痞子的
Tear gas, smoke. Hippie control.

980
01:11:23,240 --> 01:11:24,570
你的要求很高喔
You're tough.

981
01:11:24,650 --> 01:11:27,160
让我告诉你 大小很重要
Let me tell you something. Size does matter.

982
01:11:27,240 --> 01:11:28,740
不要信别人说不重要
Don't let anyone tell you different.

983
01:11:29,160 --> 01:11:32,450
这是M134机枪
This is an M134 7.62 Minigun.

984
01:11:32,540 --> 01:11:36,000
6根独立枪管 一枪就能让人烟消云散
Six individual barrels. The torso taker, powder maker.

985
01:11:36,080 --> 01:11:40,670
士兵都戏称为电蚊香或泡泡龙
Our boys in uniform call it Uncle Gazpacho, or Puff the Magic Dragon.

986
01:11:43,670 --> 01:11:44,760
好吧
Okay.

987
01:11:46,680 --> 01:11:50,470
这些是顶级古巴雪茄 高希霸 蒙特克里斯托
