史丹议员跟我在一起
I got Senator Stern here.

1187
01:27:34,500 --> 01:27:36,830
我想让他看看钢铁士兵
Thought we'd swing over and look at some of the drone designs.

1188
01:27:36,960 --> 01:27:39,210
钢铁士兵还没准备好
The drone is not going to be ready.

1189
01:27:39,500 --> 01:27:40,710
