And his shoes. Take his shoes.

1206
01:28:55,750 --> 01:28:57,410
我拿走你的东西
I took your stuff.

1207
01:28:57,500 --> 01:29:00,670
感觉怎样？很不爽吗？
How does that make you feel? Do you feel bad?

1208
01:29:01,420 --> 01:29:04,090
很好 因为我也超不爽的！
Good. 'Cause that's how I feel!

1209
