And if it hadn't, I'd be at your mercy tonight.

1217
01:29:32,620 --> 01:29:36,370
现在我拥有改良版的史氏科技
Now I have a piece of Stark tech that I pimped out myself.

1218
01:29:36,620 --> 01:29:38,370
你那高价的的钢铁士兵
And now your overpriced paperweights

1219
01:29:38,450 --> 01:29:41,040
只能当我的作为示范布景的道具
are gonna look like a backdrop to my demonstration.

1220
01:29:41,540 --> 01:29:43,790
你懂我的意思吗？
Do you dig what I'm getting at here?

1221
01:29:46,000 --> 01:29:50,300
也许你还没搞清楚 我听不懂俄文！
I don't know if you know this, but I don't speak Russian!

1222
01:29:53,680 --> 01:29:55,550
我现在要离开
I'm gonna leave now.

1223
01:29:55,640 --> 01:29:58,720
我要去参加博览会了 搞不好能泡到MM
I'm gonna go to the Expo. Maybe I'll even get laid.

1224
01:29:59,480 --> 01:30:01,310
这些家伙是你的保母
You see these guys? They're your babysitters.

1225
01:30:01,480 --> 01:30:03,980
千万别惹毛他们
They are not to be trifled with.

1226
01:30:04,360 --> 01:30:06,230
等我回来再重新谈
When I get back, we're gonna renegotiate

1227
01:30:06,320 --> 01:30:08,650
合约的条件
the terms of our agreement.

1228
01:30:09,240 --> 01:30:11,320
你一定要做到你答应做的事
And you're gonna make good on our arrangement

1229
01:30:11,820 --> 01:30:12,950
要是你做不到
because if you don't,

1230
01:30:13,030 --> 01:30:15,450
你就会跟以前我发现你时一样
you're gonna be exactly what you were when I found you,

1231
01:30:15,530 --> 01:30:17,200
是个死人
a dead man.

1232
01:30:17,330 --> 01:30:18,700
懂了吗？
You got that?

1233
01:30:19,660 --> 01:30:22,000
也许你能在电视上看到我
Maybe you can watch me on TV.

1234
01:30:31,420 --> 01:30:33,800
老兄 能把这里打扫干净吗？晕死我了
Dummy, you, can we clean up this mess? You're killing me.

1235
01:30:33,890 --> 01:30:35,300
-你知道我不…  -来电了
-You know I don't... -Incoming call

1236
01:30:35,390 --> 01:30:37,140
未显示号码 长官
with a blocked number, sir.

1237
