我又可以接电话了 太好了
My phone privilege is reinstated. Lovely.

1238
01:30:40,520 --> 01:30:41,980
考森 迷人仙境如何？
Coulson. How's the Land of Enchantment?

1239
01:30:42,060 --> 01:30:44,770
托尼 你好吗？
Hey, Tony, how you doing?

1240
01:30:46,360 --> 01:30:48,400
-我加倍了转速 -什么？
-I double cycle. -You what?

1241
01:30:49,400 --> 01:30:53,280
你叫我加倍转速制造更多能量 很好的建议
You told me double cycle's more power. Good advice.

1242
01:30:53,610 --> 01:30:55,280
你这死人头听起来精神很好
You sound pretty sprightly for a dead guy.

1243
01:30:55,360 --> 01:30:56,870
你也是
You, too.

1244
01:30:59,450 --> 01:31:00,790
-追踪来电 -先生
-Trace him. -Sir.

1245
01:31:00,870 --> 01:31:04,620
斯塔克的家族史将被改写
Now, the true history of Stark name will be written.

1246
01:31:04,710 --> 01:31:05,790
贾维斯 他在哪里？
Jarvis, where is he?

1247
01:31:05,880 --> 01:31:10,000
进入甲骨文电话网络 美国东岸
Accessing the Oracle grid. Eastern Seaboard.

1248
01:31:10,090 --> 01:31:14,220
你爸在40年闲对我家族做的事
What your father did to my family over 40 years,

1249
01:31:15,050 --> 01:31:17,720
我会在40分钟内对你做完
I will do to you in 40 minutes.

1250
01:31:17,890 --> 01:31:19,810
听起来不错 咱们好好聊聊
Sounds good. Let's get together and hash it out.

1251
01:31:20,100 --> 01:31:21,430
三州地区
Tri-State area.

1252
01:31:21,560 --> 01:31:23,770
曼哈顿和邻近行政区
Manhattan and outlying boroughs.

1253
01:31:23,890 --> 01:31:25,770
希望你准备好了
I hope you're ready.

1254
