And assemble the suit while you're at it. Put it together now.

1258
01:31:46,790 --> 01:31:49,250
-我们不确定… -我不想听到这些 贾维斯
-We are unclear as to the effects... -I don't want to hear it, Jarvis.

1259
01:31:53,630 --> 01:31:55,720
味道像椰子
That tastes like coconut.

1260
01:31:55,800 --> 01:31:57,510
还有金属
And metal.

1261
01:31:57,840 --> 01:31:59,430
哇 好！
Oh, wow, yeah!

1262
01:32:12,020 --> 01:32:13,860
我会把车停在这里
I'll keep the car down here, all right?

1263
01:32:13,940 --> 01:32:15,240
谢了 哈皮
Thank you, Happy.

1264
01:32:15,320 --> 01:32:20,120
…贾斯汀・汉默 他的展示会即将在主厅举行
...Justin Hammer. His presentation will begin shortly in the main pavilion.

1265
01:32:38,550 --> 01:32:39,800
好！
Yeah.

1266
01:32:40,970 --> 01:32:44,310
这样才对嘛 多谢光临
That's what I'm talking about. Thanks for coming.

1267
01:32:44,890 --> 01:32:46,850
