and we thought the days of losing lives were behind us.

1271
01:32:57,860 --> 01:33:00,610
但是他却不肯公开先进科技
Sadly, that technology was kept out of reach.

1272
01:33:00,700 --> 01:33:03,030
这不公平 也不对
That's not fair. That's not right.

1273
01:33:03,120 --> 01:33:05,370
-而且太可惜了 -天啊
-And it's just too bad. -Oh, Lord.

1274
01:33:05,450 --> 01:33:07,540
不过那仍是很棒的发明
Regardless, it was an impressive innovation,

1275
01:33:07,620 --> 01:33:10,540
成为世界各地的头条新闻
one that grabbed headlines the world over.

1276
01:33:10,920 --> 01:33:12,540
今天 朋友们
Well, today, my friends,

1277
01:33:12,630 --> 01:33:16,090
各大报社的麻烦大了
the press is faced with quite a different problem.

1278
01:33:16,590 --> 01:33:19,090
他们的油墨将不够用
They are about to run out of ink.

1279
01:33:24,640 --> 01:33:26,600
把这玩意移开
Get that out of here.

1280
01:33:27,560 --> 01:33:29,430
各位先生女士
Ladies and gentlemen,

1281
01:33:30,480 --> 01:33:32,850
今天我将为大家介绍
today I present to you

1282
01:33:33,150 --> 01:33:36,320
美国军方全新的面孔
the new face of the United States military.

1283
01:33:37,690 --> 01:33:38,990
汉默钢铁士兵！
The Hammer drone.

1284
01:33:41,530 --> 01:33:42,950
陆军钢铁士兵！
Army!

1285
01:33:56,090 --> 01:33:57,250
海军钢铁士兵！
Navy!

1286
01:34:07,470 --> 01:34:08,930
空军钢铁士兵！
Air Force!

1287
01:34:16,820 --> 01:34:18,110
海军陆战队钢铁士兵！
Marines!

1288
01:34:30,000 --> 01:34:32,620
好！
Yeah!

1289
01:34:36,290 --> 01:34:39,210
它们比啦啦队员好太多了 我来告诉你
That's a hell of a lot better than some cheerleaders, let me tell you.

1290
01:34:40,340 --> 01:34:43,220
虽然这是革命性的科技
But as revolutionary as this technology is,

1291
01:34:43,300 --> 01:34:47,010
