there will always be a need for man to be present in the theatre of war.

1292
01:34:47,600 --> 01:34:50,640
女士们先生们 我很荣幸能介绍
Ladies and gentlemen, today I am proud to present to you

1293
01:34:50,730 --> 01:34:52,480
第一个原型
the very first prototype

1294
01:34:52,560 --> 01:34:55,850
全面性威胁反应战斗盔甲装
in the Variable Threat Response Battle Suit

1295
01:34:55,940 --> 01:34:59,770
以及它的驾驶员-空军中校詹姆斯・罗德
and its pilot, Air Force Lieutenant Colonel James Rhodes.

1296
01:35:01,320 --> 01:35:08,450
什么？
What?

1297
01:35:24,470 --> 01:35:27,640
汉默工业向美国和盟国报到…
For America and its allies, Hammer Industries is reporting for...

1298
01:35:43,780 --> 01:35:45,450
麻烦大了
We got trouble.

1299
01:35:45,530 --> 01:35:47,240
托尼 这里有平民
Tony, there are civilians present.

1300
01:35:47,320 --> 01:35:49,950
我是奉命行事 别在这里开打
I'm here on orders. Let's not do this right now.

1301
01:35:50,030 --> 01:35:51,330
向他们挥手
Give them a wave.

1302
01:35:51,410 --> 01:35:53,580
嘿 没事
Hey, all right. Yeah.

1303
01:35:53,660 --> 01:35:55,710
大家都有危险 我们得救他们
All these people are in danger. We gotta get them out of here.

1304
01:35:55,790 --> 01:35:57,790
现在你一定要信任我
You gotta trust me for the next five minutes.

1305
01:35:57,880 --> 01:35:59,960
我试过 结果在你家被打得很惨
Yeah, I tried that. I got tossed around your house, remember?

1306
01:36:00,040 --> 01:36:02,090
听好 我认为他和万科合作
Listen, I think he's working with Vanko.

1307
01:36:02,170 --> 01:36:03,800
万科还活着？
Vanko's alive?

1308
01:36:06,260 --> 01:36:07,510
他在哪里？
Where is he?

1309
01:36:07,890 --> 01:36:09,890
-什么？  -万科在哪里？
-What? -Where's Vanko?

1310
01:36:10,350 --> 01:36:11,640
-谁？  -告诉我
-Who? -Tell me.

1311
01:36:12,260 --> 01:36:14,270
你跑来干嘛 老兄？
What are you doing here, man?

1312
01:36:18,310 --> 01:36:18,970
“瞄准”

1313
01:36:20,400 --> 01:36:22,820
