Let's take it outside.

1317
01:36:39,880 --> 01:36:40,610
“出动”

1318
01:36:44,960 --> 01:36:46,210
不 不！
No. No!

1319
01:36:56,180 --> 01:36:59,390
-贾维斯 骇进他的电脑 -遵命 长官
-Jarvis, break in. I need to own him. -Yes, sir.

1320
01:37:01,230 --> 01:37:04,150
托尼 我锁定目标了
Tony, Tony, I'm locked on. I have target lock.

1321
01:37:04,230 --> 01:37:05,900
-目标是谁？  -你！
-On what? -On you.

1322
01:37:10,910 --> 01:37:12,740
托尼 我在你后面！
Tony, on your six!

1323
01:37:30,090 --> 01:37:32,430
-发生什么事？ -软体被更改了
-What's going on? What's happening? -The software's been overridden.

1324
01:37:32,550 --> 01:37:33,760
什么？被更改是什么意思？
What? What do you mean it's been overridden?

1325
01:37:33,850 --> 01:37:35,180
-是什么意思？ -他控制了钢铁士兵
-What does that mean? -I think he slaved the drones.

1326
01:37:35,260 --> 01:37:36,350
不可能
That's impossible.

1327
01:37:36,430 --> 01:37:38,100
-打给警卫 -电话线全都被切断 长官
-Call the guards. -All the phones are down, sir.

1328
01:37:38,230 --> 01:37:40,350
那就打给他们的手机
Well, then call their... Call their cells.

1329
01:37:40,440 --> 01:37:41,940
手机也没有讯号
Their cell phones are not working, either, sir.

1330
01:37:42,060 --> 01:37:43,270
我们被档在主机外面
He's locked us out of the mainframe.

1331
01:37:43,360 --> 01:37:44,520
谁把你们挡在主机外面？
Who's locked you out of the mainframe?

1332
01:37:44,610 --> 01:37:46,190
借光 借光 走开 走开
Please, please, go away. Go away.

1333
01:37:46,280 --> 01:37:47,610
-我可以搞定 -是吗？
-I've got this handled. -Have you now?

1334
01:37:47,690 --> 01:37:48,780
当然了
Yes, I do.

1335
01:37:48,900 --> 01:37:51,360
钢铁侠不来就不会发生这种事
In fact, if your guy hadn't showed up, this wouldn't be happening.

1336
01:37:51,450 --> 01:37:53,780
拜托你走开 谢谢你
So please, now go away. Thank you.

1337
01:37:54,200 --> 01:37:56,530
我们得把那两个臭婆娘弄走
Listen, we got to get these bitches out of here.

1338
01:37:56,740 --> 01:37:58,200
什么？
What?

1339
01:37:58,290 --> 01:37:59,620
告诉我是谁在搞鬼
You tell me who's behind this.

1340
01:37:59,710 --> 01:38:04,250
-谁在搞鬼？ -伊万 伊万万科
-Who's behind this? -Ivan. Ivan Vanko.

1341
01:38:04,630 --> 01:38:07,250
-他在哪里？ -他在我的公司
-Where is he? -He's at my facility.

1342
01:38:10,590 --> 01:38:12,220
-请帮我接纽约警局总部 -不 不 不！
-I need NYPD, please. -No, no, no!

1343
01:38:12,300 --> 01:38:13,470
-指挥中心 -不 不 亲爱的
-Command Central. -No, no, honey.

1344
01:38:13,590 --> 01:38:15,470
-不！别打给警方 -好 马上 马上
-Don't call the authorities. -Okay. Right away. Right away.

1345
01:38:15,600 --> 01:38:17,640
让开！让开！
Step aside. Step aside.

1346
01:38:18,600 --> 01:38:20,270
告诉我你知道的一切
Tell me everything you know. Go.

1347
01:38:27,650 --> 01:38:30,650
-贾维斯 情况如何？ -无法远端重新开机
-How are we doing, Jarvis? -Remote reboot unsuccessful.

1348
01:38:48,170 --> 01:38:49,670
从这里
This way.

1349
01:38:50,340 --> 01:38:52,170
发生什么事？
Nobody's answering the phone. What's going on?

1350
01:38:52,260 --> 01:38:54,510
上车 载我到汉默工业
Get in the car. Take me to Hammer Industries.

1351
01:38:54,590 --> 01:38:57,010
-我才不要载你 -好吧 你要我开车吗？
-I'm not taking you anywhere. -Fine. You want me to drive?

1352
01:38:57,100 --> 01:38:59,640
不 我来开 上车
No, I'm driving. Get in the car.

1353
01:39:24,960 --> 01:39:26,040
“失去连线”

1354
01:39:58,070 --> 01:39:59,740
干得好 小鬼
Nice work, kid.

1355
01:40:01,540 --> 01:40:04,870
-多具钢铁士兵在追你 -我们离博览会愈远愈好
-You got multiples coming in on you. -Let's get this away from the Expo.

1356
01:40:10,250 --> 01:40:12,670
到了以后我要你守住外面
When we arrive, I need you to watch the perimeter.

1357
01:40:12,760 --> 01:40:16,420
我要进去消灭目标
I'm gonna enter the facility and take down the target.

1358
01:40:18,720 --> 01:40:21,350
-眼睛看前面！  -知道了啦
-Watch the road. -I got it. I got it.

1359
01:40:43,370 --> 01:40:45,080
“失去连线”

1360
01:40:51,750 --> 01:40:52,790
听好
Listen, listen.

1361
01:40:52,920 --> 01:40:54,920
一群钢铁士兵刚脱队 它们飞回博览会
A pack just peeled off. They're headed back to the Expo.

1362
01:40:55,010 --> 01:40:56,340
收到
Got it.

1363
01:41:00,140 --> 01:41:01,590
我正逼近你！
I'm closing on you.

1364
01:41:01,680 --> 01:41:04,100
准备向你开火！托尼 小心！
Ordnance coming in hot, Tony. Watch it.

1365
01:41:19,950 --> 01:41:22,620
-待在车上 -我才不要待在车上
-Stay in the car. -I'm not staying in the car.

1366
01:41:22,700 --> 01:41:24,280
我叫你待在车上
I said, stay in the car.

1367
01:41:24,450 --> 01:41:26,450
你穿的是什么？
What are you wearing?

1368
01:41:27,700 --> 01:41:30,000
我不能让你一个人进去
Look, I'm not letting you go in there alone.

1369
01:41:30,120 --> 01:41:31,500
你想帮忙？别让车子熄火
You want to help? Keep the car running.

1370
01:41:31,630 --> 01:41:32,880
好吧
Okay.

1371
01:41:33,840 --> 01:41:35,450
“外人侵入”

1372
01:41:36,380 --> 01:41:38,670
你们不能进来！
You can't come in here.

1373
01:41:39,130 --> 01:41:40,680
稳住
Hold on. Hey!

1374
01:42:21,380 --> 01:42:22,040
“出动”

1375
01:42:25,390 --> 01:42:27,310
每组钢铁士兵
Each set of drones is communicating

1376
01:42:27,390 --> 01:42:30,140
-用自己的语言沟通 -挑一组 阻止它们
-in its own unique language. -Well, choose one and focus on that.

1377
01:42:30,230 --> 01:42:32,230
你们试过俄语了吗？你们怎么不试试俄语？
Have you tried Russian? Why don't you try Russian?

1378
01:42:35,900 --> 01:42:38,270
注意 我们已经侵入了网格W
Attention. We have intrusion on Grid W.

1379
01:42:38,360 --> 01:42:40,610
收到 我们已经开始了
We got it. We're on our way.

1380
01:43:22,070 --> 01:43:23,490
我摇倒他了！
I got him!

1381
01:43:38,340 --> 01:43:40,380
-洛德 你还在锁定我吗？  -对
-Rhodey, you still locked on? -Yeah.

1382
01:43:40,460 --> 01:43:43,970
穿好雨衣 我们就要洗澡了
Drop your socks and grab your Crocs. We're about to get wet on this ride.

1383
01:43:46,130 --> 01:43:47,260
等等…等等…
Wait, wait, wait!

1384
01:44:06,820 --> 01:44:08,280
他离开了！
He's gone.

1385
01:44:12,330 --> 01:44:14,370
抱歉 我得减少敌人数量
I'm sorry, buddy. Had to thin out the herd.

1386
01:44:15,160 --> 01:44:17,000
你在哪里？
What's your 20?

1387
01:44:28,640 --> 01:44:31,470
-你在干嘛？ -替洛德的战斗装重新开机
-What are you doing? -I'm rebooting Rhodey's suit.

1388
01:44:37,850 --> 01:44:38,890
托尼！
Tony!

1389
01:44:45,530 --> 01:44:46,270
“准许进入”

1390
01:44:55,410 --> 01:44:57,080
完成重新开机
Reboot complete.

1391
01:44:57,750 --> 01:44:59,500
你的好麻吉回来了
You got your best friend back.

1392
01:44:59,580 --> 01:45:02,960
-多谢了 罗曼诺夫特工 -你的全新能量板很棒
-Thank you very much, Agent Romanoff. -Well done with the new chest piece.

1393
01:45:03,050 --> 01:45:06,710
我发现输出的能量更强了 你的生命迹象也很正常
I am reading significantly higher output and your vitals all look promising.

1394
01:45:06,800 --> 01:45:09,550
是啊 我暂时死不了 谢了
Yes, for the moment, I'm not dying. Thank you.

1395
01:45:09,640 --> 01:45:11,720
什么意思？你本来快死了？
What do you mean you're not dying? Did you just say you're dying?

1396
01:45:11,800 --> 01:45:13,550
是你吗？不 我没死
Is that you? No, I'm not.

1397
01:45:13,640 --> 01:45:15,180
-我不会死了 -发生什么事？
-Not any more. -What's going on?

1398
01:45:15,270 --> 01:45:17,020
我本来要告诉你
I was going to tell you. I didn't want to alarm you.

1399
01:45:17,100 --> 01:45:18,600
你要告诉我？你本来要死吗？
You were gonna tell me? You really were dying?

1400
01:45:18,730 --> 01:45:20,440
-你没给我机会说 -你为什么不告诉我？
-You didn't let me. -Why didn't you tell me that?

1401
01:45:20,560 --> 01:45:23,270
上次煎蛋卷的时候本来要说
I was gonna make you an omelette and tell you.

1402
01:45:23,400 --> 01:45:26,320
你们等度蜜月再聊吧 敌人来袭 托尼
Hey, hey. Save it for the honeymoon. You got incoming, Tony.

1403
01:45:26,400 --> 01:45:27,990
看来它们盯上你了
Looks like the fight's coming to you.

1404
01:45:28,070 --> 01:45:29,900
-太棒了 小辣椒？ -你现在没事了？
-Great. Pepper? -Are you okay now?

1405
01:45:29,990 --> 01:45:31,200
我没事 别生气
I am fine. Don't be mad.

1406
01:45:31,280 --> 01:45:32,870
-我正式道歉… -我很生气
-I will formally apologise... -I am mad!

1407
01:45:32,950 --> 01:45:35,910
先等我闪避攻击再说
...when I'm not fending off a Hammeroid attack.

1408
01:45:35,990 --> 01:45:37,410
-好吧 -我们本来是在威尼斯的
-Fine. -We could have been in Venice.

1409
01:45:37,500 --> 01:45:38,540
噢 拜托
Oh, please.

1410
01:45:41,920 --> 01:45:43,290
洛德！
Rhodes?

1411
01:45:43,750 --> 01:45:46,420
快醒醒 我需要你
Snap out of it, buddy. I need you.

1412
01:45:47,170 --> 01:45:49,470
它们攻来了 快醒过来
They're coming. Come on, let's roll. Get up.

1413
01:45:52,760 --> 01:45:54,930
你可以把钢铁盔甲拿回去
Oh, man. You can have your suit back.

1414
01:45:58,430 --> 01:45:59,770
你没事吧？
You okay?

1415
01:45:59,940 --> 01:46:01,480
没事 谢了
Yeah, thanks.

1416
01:46:03,020 --> 01:46:05,440
-托尼 听好 很抱歉 -别道歉
-Tony, look, I'm sorry, okay? -Don't be.

1417
01:46:05,520 --> 01:46:06,730
我应该更信任你
No. I should have trusted you more.

1418
01:46:06,820 --> 01:46:08,400
是我害你的 算了吧
I'm the one who put you in this position. Forget it.

1419
01:46:08,490 --> 01:46:10,820
对 是你的错 我只想说声抱歉
No. It's your fault. I just wanted to say I'm sorry.

1420
01:46:10,950 --> 01:46:14,200
谢了 我也只想听你这么说 伙伴
Thank you. That's all I wanted to hear. Partner.

1421
01:46:14,450 --> 01:46:18,040
它们正在追来 有什么对策？
They're coming in hot, any second. What's the play?

1422
01:46:18,660 --> 01:46:20,290
我们要到制高点
Well, we want to take the high ground, okay?

1423
01:46:20,370 --> 01:46:21,960
把最猛的大炮带到山脊
So let's put the biggest gun up on that ridge.

1424
01:46:22,040 --> 01:46:23,330
收到
Got you.

1425
01:46:24,170 --> 01:46:25,250
-那你要去哪里？ -你要去哪里？
-Where do you want to be? -Where are you going?

1426
01:46:25,340 --> 01:46:26,960
-你在说什么？ -我是说我啦
-What're you talking about? -I meant me.

1427
01:46:27,050 --> 01:46:29,050
你是有一支大炮 但不是最猛的
You have a big gun. You are not the big gun.

1428
01:46:29,130 --> 01:46:30,510
-托尼 别嫉妒我 -不 是低调
-Tony, don't be jealous. -No. It's subtle,

1429
01:46:30,630 --> 01:46:31,760
-全身挂满了东东 -是的
-all the bells and whistles. -Yeah.

1430
01:46:31,840 --> 01:46:34,340
-我这才叫狠角色  -好吧
-It's called being a badass. -Fine.

1431
01:46:35,050 --> 01:46:38,430
你到制高点 我把它们引来
All right. You go up top. I'll draw them in.

1432
01:46:38,520 --> 01:46:40,390
别待在这里 太危险了
Don't stay down here. This is the worst place to be.

1433
01:46:40,480 --> 01:46:41,730
你有地方去 那我呢？
Okay, you got a spot. Where's mine?

1434
01:46:41,810 --> 01:46:45,970
这里是杀戮区 托尼 待在这里必死无疑
It's the kill box, Tony. Okay? This is where you go to die.

1435
01:47:34,530 --> 01:47:36,240
-看到没？  -有 好样的
-See that? -Yeah, yeah, nice.

1436
01:47:44,250 --> 01:47:45,540
洛德…
Rhodey?

1437
01:47:46,880 --> 01:47:48,380
趴下来！
Get down.

1438
01:47:58,600 --> 01:48:01,060
下次你应该先用这招
Wow. I think you should lead with that next time.

1439
01:48:01,140 --> 01:48:04,480
抱歉 老板 这招只能用一次 这是一次性的
Yeah. Sorry, boss. I can only use it once. It's a one-off.

1440
01:48:06,900 --> 01:48:09,060
我5分钟前就跟你说了
I told you that five minutes ago.

1441
01:48:10,400 --> 01:48:11,770
你要抓的就是他
That's your guy here.

1442
01:48:13,110 --> 01:48:15,110
-说什么？ -先生 你被捕了
-Excuse me? -You're being placed under arrest.

1443
01:48:15,240 --> 01:48:16,650
-你在开玩笑吧？  -手放在背后
-Are you kidding me? -Hands behind your back, sir.

1444
01:48:16,740 --> 01:48:18,410
我想帮忙
I'm trying to help here.

1445
01:48:22,490 --> 01:48:26,040
我明白 我知道你的诡计 你想把一切都归罪于我吗？
I get it. I see what you're doing. You're trying to pin this on me, huh?

1446
01:48:26,120 --> 01:48:27,710
好样的
That's good. That's good.

1447
01:48:27,790 --> 01:48:30,750
你开始像首席执行官一样思考 铲除竞争对手
You're starting to think like a CEO, taking out the competition.

1448
01:48:30,920 --> 01:48:33,300
我喜欢 你以为你让我惹上大麻烦？
I like that. You think you're making a problem for me?

1449
01:48:33,420 --> 01:48:34,460
我才要让你惹上大麻烦
I'm gonna make a problem for you.

1450
01:48:34,590 --> 01:48:37,590
我们很快会再见面
I'm gonna be seeing you again real soon.

1451
01:48:41,760 --> 01:48:43,260
他们赶来以后 你应该请他们守在
When they get here, I think you should station them

1452
01:48:43,350 --> 01:48:46,180
东南和西方两个出口
at the south, east and both west exits.

1453
01:48:46,270 --> 01:48:48,350
我们关闭了七号线地铁
We shut down the 7 train in and out of Willets Point already.

1454
01:48:48,440 --> 01:48:51,230
派公车载人接驳没关闭的地铁
Well, have city buses there to ferry people to operating lines.

1455
01:48:51,310 --> 01:48:52,820
好 你要一起来吗？
Yeah. Are you coming with us?

1456
01:48:52,940 --> 01:48:56,400
-不 我要等到大家都疏散了 -好吧
-No, I'm gonna stay till the park is clear. -Okay.

1457
01:48:58,150 --> 01:49:00,660
小心 一个钢铁士兵来袭
Heads up. You got one more drone incoming.

1458
01:49:00,780 --> 01:49:02,120
这一个看起来不太一样
This one looks different.

1459
01:49:02,580 --> 01:49:04,950
能量指数特别高
The repulsor signature is significantly higher.

1460
01:49:16,050 --> 01:49:17,720
回来真好
Good to be back.

1461
01:49:18,300 --> 01:49:19,680
情况不妙
This ain't gonna be good.

1462
01:49:23,220 --> 01:49:25,310
我要用特别的武器对付他
I got something special for this guy.

1463
01:49:25,470 --> 01:49:27,600
让我用“前妻”把他打爆
I'm gonna bust his bunker with the Ex-Wife.

1464
01:49:27,680 --> 01:49:29,140
用什么？
With the what?

1465
01:49:39,530 --> 01:49:42,030
-汉默的武器？ -对
-Hammer tech? -Yeah.

1466
01:49:43,870 --> 01:49:45,450
让我来吧
I got this.

1467
01:50:38,380 --> 01:50:40,380
罗德 我有个点子
Rhodes. I got an idea.

1468
01:50:40,760 --> 01:50:43,260
-你想当英雄吗？ -什么？
-You want to be a hero? -What?

1469
01:50:43,590 --> 01:50:46,550
我需要一个助手 举起手
I could really use a sidekick. Put your hand up.

1470
01:50:46,640 --> 01:50:48,510
-这就是你的点子？ -对
-This is your idea? -Yep.

1471
01:50:49,220 --> 01:50:51,810
我准备好了 来吧…
I'm ready. I'm ready. Go, go, go!

1472
01:50:55,610 --> 01:50:56,690
发射！
Take it.

1473
01:51:25,260 --> 01:51:26,680
你输了
You lose.

1474
01:51:34,230 --> 01:51:36,980
钢铁士兵都会自爆 我们得赶快闪人
All these drones are rigged to blow. We gotta get out of here, man.

1475
01:51:37,480 --> 01:51:38,730
小辣椒？
Pepper?

1476
01:52:18,900 --> 01:52:20,650
天啊 我受不了了
Oh, my God! I can't take this any more.

1477
01:52:20,730 --> 01:52:22,150
-你受不了？  -我受不了了
-You can't? -I can't take this.

1478
01:52:22,230 --> 01:52:23,650
-看着我 -我的身体 字面意思
-Look at me. -My body, literally,

1479
01:52:23,740 --> 01:52:24,990
承受不了这种压力
cannot handle the stress.

1480
01:52:25,070 --> 01:52:29,570
我永远不知道你会不会死或是毁了整家公司
I never know if you're gonna kill yourself or wreck the whole company.

1481
01:52:29,660 --> 01:52:31,660
我想我做得不错
I think I did okay.

1482
01:52:31,830 --> 01:52:33,870
老娘不干了 我要辞职
I quit. I'm resigning.

1483
01:52:34,500 --> 01:52:35,870
就是这样
That's it.

1484
01:52:36,460 --> 01:52:39,040
你说什么？你不干了？
What did you just say? You're done?

1485
01:52:40,340 --> 01:52:43,840
这倒是很令人惊讶 不 这不奇怪 我了解
That's surprising. No, it's not surprising. I get it.

1486
01:52:44,260 --> 01:52:47,550
-你不必找藉口 -我…我…我并没有找藉口
-You don't have to make any excuses. -I'm... I'm... I'm not making any excuses.

1487
01:52:47,630 --> 01:52:48,760
你是真的在找藉口
You actually were just making excuses.

1488
01:52:48,840 --> 01:52:50,340
-其实你无需这样 -不 我没有找藉口
